甸人民的各項援助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2021/02/1612480756237-f753e4a3f04f4995a1dba2b0a3f19da1-800x533.jpg?unShow=false\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2021%2F02%2F1612480756237-f753e4a3f04f4995a1dba2b0a3f19da1-800x533.jpg%3FunShow%3Dfalse&h=28af43e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／美聯社／達志影像<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/5187239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F5187239&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=f39689cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/5187239</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:46:03.000Z","msg":"收皮啦佢 佢都冇權力去決定"},{"pid":"dc239dd404459fe78f6bfb0f607098c711b52c6e","tid":2403053,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:20:54.000Z","msg":"幾時會凍結共匪黨員在美資產？"}]}